# CLIP ChangeLog for sys-apps/sysvinit

*sysvinit-2.88-r12 (29 Feb 2016)

  29 Feb 2016; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +sysvinit-2.88-r12.ebuild, -sysvinit-2.88-r11.ebuild:
  Remove tty2 on clip-bare; for now only one console login
  at a time.

  19 Feb 2016; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  sysvinit-2.88-r11.ebuild:
  Migrate from clip-tiny to clip-bare.

*sysvinit-2.88-r11 (12 Oct 2015)

  12 Oct 2015; Alain Ozanne <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +sysvinit-2.88-r11.ebuild, -sysvinit-2.88-r10.ebuild:
  Update dependency to virtual/os-headers.

*sysvinit-2.88-r10 (28 Sep 2015)

  28 Sep 2015; Alain Ozanne <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +sysvinit-2.88-r10.ebuild, -sysvinit-2.88-r9.ebuild:
  Update dependency on linux-headers when compiling for clip-devstation.

*sysvinit-2.88-r9 (13 Mar 2015)

  13 Mar 2015; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +sysvinit-2.88-r9.ebuild, -sysvinit-2.88-r8.ebuild:
  Fix tty serial terminal creation (ARM only).
  Fix login.tty script for clip-tiny.

*sysvinit-2.88-r8 (29 Jul 2014)

  04 Mar 2015; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  sysvinit-2.88-r8.ebuild:
  Fix tty terminals creation on clip-tiny (=> no need to bump).

  29 Jul 2014; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +sysvinit-2.88-r8.ebuild, -sysvinit-2.88-r7.ebuild, -files/login.livecd,
